full_text:
Hi Ann,

Just jumping in to add my two cents. I personally don&#39;t like to focus 
on evil entities, even though I believe 100% that lower astrals 
exist. Not only that, Tibetan shamans, among others, have repeatedly 
shown that thought forms can be given form and a measure of life. 

The way I see it, if we keep a higher focus, such things as rage, 
hate, and destruction among other things will be far removed. Ouija 
Boards have many times been the source of horrible experiences. Just 
from listening to all the hundreds of callers on C2C over the years, 
I&#39;d say over 95% of the stories weren&#39;t good. 

George did make a good statement to the effect that it&#39;s not good 
giving a loaded gun to a child.  

Lance

